title: Stanford, Princeton scientists launch MedOS AI-XR-cobot clinical system
description:
MedOS, which the Stanford-Princeton AI Coscientist Team is building from data from multiple sources, is designed to facilitate robot aid in clinical settings.

The post Stanford, Princeton scientists launch MedOS AI-XR-cobot clinical system appeared first on The Robot Report.
